Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101664,103666}"Cherry blossom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105001,107462}We learned it in\NEnglish class, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107920,109631}It's the English\Nwords for "Sakura".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110715,112216}Oh, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:55.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112467,115136}There's a painting\Ncalled "Cherry Blossom"…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:56.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115219,116679}at the Central Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116763,118514}Oh, I know about that painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:03.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119307,123311}Isn't that the masterpiece\Nso admired…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:06.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123394,126105}for it's life-like\Nwithering petals?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:09.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126397,129359}I'd like to see it once myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:12.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130443,132820}You're going to steal the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132904,134739}Rather, I'd like you to get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134781,136157}Get it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:22.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137784,142038}An old man came to me\Nfor help yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:29.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143873,149629}He says that the owner\Nof the museum deceived him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149754,151255}Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152048,154467}The old man thought\Nhe signed a contract…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154509,156803}to loan "Cherry Blossom"\Nto the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:41.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157428,161391}Later he found out they had\Nswitched the contract to one…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:44.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161474,164060}that transferred ownership\Nof the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:49.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167188,169691}What is that?! How mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:55.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170066,175279}The modern art exhibition\Nhas just opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175697,177031}So during the…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:58.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177198,178574}I get the idea, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178991,181786}Just leave the rest to St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:07.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184622,187792}New Student Rina.\NA Formidable Enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:15.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194882,195967}Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196008,197719}I still can't beat this game!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:18.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197802,198594}Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:21.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198636,201723}And I've used up\Nthis month's allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202265,203891}Hey, where's Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:25.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204058,205268}Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:27.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205935,207937}He's been like that the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:36.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215403,216154}Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216195,218906}Hey, I think you\Nshould retreat a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:39.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218990,219991}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:45.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222869,225538}That's from you butting in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226122,227832}No, dodge those!\NAnd those, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:48.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227874,228791}And those, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228833,230042}Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230126,231961}Now, punch!\NNo, dodge again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232003,233129}What are you doing?!\NKick! Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233212,234464}Jump! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234547,236007}Go now! Do it! Do…!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236048,237258}Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238718,240720}Quit your yakking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:05.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242764,245767}You're so frustrating.\NHere, let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:08.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246350,248019}What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252565,254025}You…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254358,255985}Bad form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256027,257779}Whose fault is that, huh?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:19.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258362,259989}Just who the heck are you anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260031,261866}Butting into other people's business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:26.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262492,266746}Your interference ruined my game!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:29.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267955,269540}Hey, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269582,271876}Hold on, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:32.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271959,272919}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274045,276923}"I'm going to the Central Museum\Ntomorrow night…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276964,278674}to get Cherry Blossom".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280092,281511}This is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283095,285389}It's a warning from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286641,287892}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:48.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287934,288851}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:49.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288893,289811}Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:53.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289936,293314}You're living in this town\Nand you don't know St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293397,294774}What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:59.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295942,299445}How rude! I just moved here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300655,302156}Hey, she's…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302949,304784}taller than me…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305660,307328}and I don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307370,309872}– I have to think up a strategy!\N– Hey, wait…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310623,311958}Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:16.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313125,316254}St. Tail, I'll get you\Nfor sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:17.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316337,317880}Hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318047,319006}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:22.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319090,322677}Sheesh, I 'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:27.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323845,327014}– I said hold on!\N– You 're annoying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331060,332937}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:44.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342822,344824}You 're not very fit, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344949,346075}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346242,349620}Hey, tell me about St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350288,351539}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352748,355209}Hey, what are you doing?!\NCut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355334,357920}So, you gonna tell me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358004,359422}Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361007,362842}Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362884,365011}Okay, I'll tell you!\NLet go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:09.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366137,369015}Ooh, that hurt.\NI thought I was gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369056,370892}I'm sorry, did that really hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370975,372143}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372226,373102}And…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:16.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373477,376439}St. Tail is a girl thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376939,379108}Oh, a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379317,381402}That means she's a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381485,382445}What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:26.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382486,386908}Her true identity is unknown. But she's\Nso sly, that the police can't catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386991,389327}The police can't catch her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393164,394457}I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394457,396918}Where's the Central Museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:41.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398085,401797}At Third Ave and Bay Street, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401923,403507}OK, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403591,405259}Sorry if I was\Na bit rough on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406010,408804}I'm Rina Takamiya.\NI'm 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:49.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408888,409972}See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411641,413309}What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414477,416729}Time to eat, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:57.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416896,417980}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418648,420441}Wow, it looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420691,421567}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:04.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423694,424654}Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425154,426405}Now call Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426656,427531}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434121,435581}You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:16.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435831,436958}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437667,438960}What am I gonna do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439752,441295}What are you doing, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441420,442880}Hmm? This.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:25.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443381,445174}Those are Tarot cards, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:26.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445257,446008}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446342,449512}I'm wondering if I can use tarot card\Nfortune-telling to do some new magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450221,453516}That sounds like fun!\NWill you try it on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453975,455184}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472076,473494}What's wrong, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:57.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475371,477081}Is anything wrong with that card?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480334,482628}Mama, don't scare us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483254,484714}Really, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484964,486841}You should keep your mind\Non the task at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487717,489427}It's time for dinner, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:10.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490052,490886}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492805,494390}What's so funny, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494515,495349}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495433,497935}It's just that you and Meimi\Ndo the things the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:18.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498019,498728}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:22.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499311,502106}I'm a little worried\Nabout Meimi, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502815,503941}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:28.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504316,508195}According to the cards,\Nshe's in for a bit of an ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509071,510197}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:35.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511198,515703}She'll be all right, because like me,\Nher best feature is her cheerfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516162,517246}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:40.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517329,520416}And besides, my bad fortune-telling\Nis probably wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521167,523711}Well, well, what's\Nfor dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:47.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524462,527631}Today it's your favorite, beef stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527715,529008}That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529091,531969}Papa, Mama, I'm gonna start eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:53.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532053,533012}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536724,538059}Oh, I'm full.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543606,545399}Come on, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:10.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546817,550863}I can't today, I've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:12.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551864,552907}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558496,559580}OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:23.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560456,563334}Oh, I forgot to ask Papa\Nabout the tarot cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563959,565169}Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565336,567213}I'll just give it\Nmy all today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:36.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573302,576597}Forgive me, for I use\Nno gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:42.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581852,582812}One…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585481,586398}Two…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588692,590194}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:09.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606001,609547}May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611882,613551}It's gonna be great today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614009,616929}Meimi, be careful tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:17.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617221,617888}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617972,620141}I feel strangely uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:24.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620641,624436}You mean Asuka Jr.?\NHe's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:30.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624687,630901}Not Asuka Jr., something else.\NSomething else is going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632444,634113}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:37.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635406,637616}So long as the blessings of God\Nare with us…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637658,639451}there's nothing\NSt. Tail can't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639910,641370}Well, I better go.
Comment: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:44.66,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:644665,644665}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:50.67,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:650671,650671}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:55.67,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:655676,655676}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:05.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664602,665561}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666937,668772}Everyone is in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:10.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669273,670816}All right, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:14.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671525,674778}If you see someone suspicious,\Ndon't let him get away, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:15.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674862,675738}We found this one loitering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:16.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675821,676614}Whaa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:17.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676780,677489}Come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677573,679825}All right, I'm coming,\Nyou don't have to pull me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:21.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680451,681452}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681869,683078}Hey, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684121,685247}It's you…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686207,688292}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:32.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688584,692922}You're in charge of security?\NWow, you're only in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693047,695966}I'm in Junior High and\NI'm the same age as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696050,697009}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697384,699386}She insists that she's\Nauthorized personnel…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699428,701472}and refuses to move\Nfrom the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701805,704141}Asuka Jr., this one is a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704433,707311}Maybe she's St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:54.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709647,714610}Take your filthy hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:59.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716528,719698}I'm going to stand\Nguard over here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:00.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719907,720741}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:06.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722993,726205}I was appointed by the Mayor\Nto investigate St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:09.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726664,729041}You can't go around doing whatever\Nyou want without my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729583,730751}The Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:12.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731794,732920}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733379,735965}The Mayor happens to be my Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736882,738676}Which makes you the Mayor's niece?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:23.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738759,743555}Yes! Besides, we've got a lot\Nof our paintings here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743806,745432}We can't have a thief breaking in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:26.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745766,746767}But… but…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747142,750145}Well, you go ahead and\Ndo what you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751230,752731}Darn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754525,755985}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:38.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756318,758320}Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775170,776588}"Cherry Blossom"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777339,779591}It's splendid, just as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785014,787933}Hey, cut it out!\NThat's so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788809,790311}You know, it's all because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791228,792438}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:15.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792813,795316}It's St. Tail.\NDon't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795399,796608}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796650,798986}Don't panic! Switch on\Nthe emergency lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801363,804241}All right! Everyone, check\Nup on your assigned posts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805075,806076}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806160,807828}Cherry Blossom is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808037,809371}It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812291,813125}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817588,819214}This is a cherry blossom petal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819340,820758}There are more\Ntrailing off that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:46.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822926,826764}If we follow the trail,\Nwe' ll run into the thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827306,829391}Hold it!\NDon't go acting on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829892,831977}Why don't you stay here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:57.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832269,837107}I have confidence in my legs and my\Nstrength, so I'll go nab the thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:13:59.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838317,839276}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:04.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841362,844823}Oh shoot! That's her way of\Nthrowing us into confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:17.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852956,857878}Hey, maybe that girl has\Nalready caught St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858045,860923}Could be. That would really\Nmake us look like fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:24.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861006,864635}All right! We'll follow the\Ncherry blossom petals! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864676,865427}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:29.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865928,869014}Darn it, I'm the one who's\Ngoing to capture St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873477,875521}Hmm… pretty good…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876313,878565}but not clever enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880734,883195}I wonder who that girl is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:49.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884905,889952}Here I have with me a piece of cloth.\NNothing up my sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:55.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893080,895791}The masterpiece, Cherry Blossom,\Nthat disappeared…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:56.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895874,896834}Appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:05.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904842,905717}Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907761,910764}As a matter of fact,\NI didn 't steal it, yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912141,914226}I'm not letting you\Nget away, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915978,917062}So, that's the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:30.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924153,930451}Hold it! Hold it! Hold it! Hold it!\NI'm the one who's capturing St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:34.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931994,934163}"Please keep the supply closet clean."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936039,938041}Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938375,940711}And just why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:44.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941086,944423}I couldn't help it.\NThe petals led me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944673,947176}This is St. Tail's usual\Nway of confusing people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:50.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947259,950179}Which means you fell for\Nthe same trick every time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952431,955142}There are more petals.\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955934,957227}Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960772,962941}Hey! Isn't this her usual trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:03.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963025,963734}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963817,966278}You are just worried about\Nyour paintings, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966403,967946}That's all you're worried about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:09.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968071,969406}What? You actually\Nbelieved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969490,970324}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970574,972993}What I told you were, obviously,\Nall lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973285,974536}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:23.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980459,983128}They say that lying makes a thief!\NEven a thief possesses an ounce of logic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:28.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983795,988467}This is absurd!\NDon 't you forget it!\NIn other words, you're pretty bad\Nat avoiding and dodging things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993138,995349}What's this?\NWe're outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:36.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995766,996725}There's something strange going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997643,1000646}Although it's not the right season,\Nthe cherry blossom is in full bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:42.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001355,1002439}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:43.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002981,1003941}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005108,1007027}Up there, on top of that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010906,1012366}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013200,1015285}St. Tail? That's her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:59.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015744,1019373}Good work. I'm taking\NCherry Blossom with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019665,1020707}Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:01.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020791,1021792}Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:09.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022626,1029216}When I grow up, I'll become a police\Nofficer. And I'll arrest St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:12.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029550,1032636}No way! If anyone arrests St. Tail,\Nit'll be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:15.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032719,1035180}It really doesn't matter\Nwho arrests her, does it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035264,1036056}Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:16.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036056,1036890}Nyaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037558,1040435}I know it's not the right season,\Nbut I'll give you two a free show…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040477,1042312}of falling cherry blossom petals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:28.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045566,1048068}It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:41.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060998,1061790}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079474,1080100}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081518,1082686}Ouch…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082978,1084855}Hey! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086315,1087357}What? Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:11.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089735,1091028}She's outwitted me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:18.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093947,1098035}Humph! She may be a thief,\Nbut she's just a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098702,1101872}If only you didn't get in my way,\NI would have captured her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:25.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103457,1105751}You really are so…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136657,1137658}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150045,1152047}Good morning, Meimi.\NYou're going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152339,1154341}Oh, good morning, Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:19.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156176,1159680}Seira… nothing happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170232,1171733}Miss Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172776,1174778}Oh, good morning, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:38.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175153,1178073}Good morning, Miss Haneoka.\NI'd like you to do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:41.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178115,1181910}This is a new student who will be in\Nyour class. Please take her with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:43.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182077,1183578}Sure, I'd be glad to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:44.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183954,1184996}Miss Takamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185038,1186957}"ST. TAIL EXPOSES MUSEUM SWINDLE\NOwner Arrested"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190335,1191086}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:55.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192295,1195632}This is Rina Takamiya, a new\Nstudent who has just arrived today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:56.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195799,1196758}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197467,1199469}She's… yesterday's…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200429,1201513}Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201722,1203682}I'll become a police officer…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209271,1211898}Please take care of her,\NMiss Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212566,1213483}Uh… yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:20.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216737,1220824}You keep staring at me.\NIs there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:25.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221575,1225537}No. I'm Meimi Haneoka,\Nglad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225954,1228206}If you ever need anything,\Njust ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228665,1230542}– Okay. I do have one question.\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:34.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231376,1234212}There's this boy I'd like\Nto meet, named Asuka Jr..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:35.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234546,1235964}Is he at this school?
